        <item>
            <title>滴滴推「经济型」选项可以不叫的士，实试叫车比 Uber 平达 20%</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/didi-vs-uber/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=didi-vs-uber</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/didi-vs-uber/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 28 Apr 2025 12:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305306</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港滴滴出行静静地推出了一款全新「经济型」私家车服务，可以不呼叫的士而呼叫经济型私家车，进一步扩展本地业务版图。新服务提供比预约的士更具吸引力的车费，与市场另一竞争者 Uber 相比，同一路线价格最多相差 20 港元。记者实测显示，滴滴经济型私家车在特定路线及时段展现出明显价格优势，预计此举将重新激起香港网约车平台的竞争格局。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05677-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305309" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05677-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05677-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05677-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲滴滴新增「经济型」车辆选项</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05679-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305307" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05679-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05679-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05679-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲在点经济型车辆后，将叫「KayGo」品牌的私家车<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-scaled.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>滴滴出行自上周五起，开始分阶段开放经济型私家车服务予香港用户。原本仅限网约的士的滴滴，现于 App 介面新增「经济型」专区，乘客可透过简单操作预约私家车，享用比的士更低的车费。根据平台资料，这类车辆由 KayGo 车队提供，该公司正积极招揽本地私家车司机，扩展服务规模。滴滴方面预告，短期内会向所有香港用户全面开放这项服务。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc05678-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>价格方面，记者于非繁忙时段实测，由观塘伟业街至旺角山东街，滴滴经济型车费约为 HK$82，Uber 同时间、同路段普通车型则收费 HK$104，如享有折扣价则为 HK$92，比起滴滴「经济型」叫车贵 10-18 元。而在滴滴叫的士的预计跳表价则为 HK$89 元起。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8177-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305312" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8177-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8177-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8177-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲叫车由观塘伟业街至旺角山东街，在记者叫车时段收费 HK$82.21，叫合作的士收费由 HK$89.05 起<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8176-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305313" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8176-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8176-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8176-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲同一时段呼叫 Uber, 未折扣前价格为 HK$104.48，如有折扣则为 HK$92.48<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_81712-scaled.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>但我们也发现 Uber 在长途车的价格反而会比滴滴「经济型」选项便宜。例如由观塘伟业街至观塘型点商场 1 期，Uber 收费在折扣前只为 HK$321，而滴滴经济型车辆则需要 HK$336。建议用户在出发前，应自行比较滴滴及 Uber 两款 App 的即时报价，以获得最抵选择。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8175-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8175-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8175-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8175-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8174-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305315" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8174-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8174-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8174-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>以上价格只供参考，实际收费以各平台叫车当时的收费为准。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/didi-vs-uber/life-tech/">滴滴推「经济型」选项可以不叫的士，实试叫车比 Uber 平达 20%</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
