        <item>
            <title>金像奖红地毡用 iPhone 做直播，两部 iPhone + MacBook 实现两小时稳定串流</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/iphone-26/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-26</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/iphone-26/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 28 Apr 2025 07:42:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影视娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305246</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>为提升户外直播稳定性及灵活性，第 43 届香港电影金像奖颁奖典礼红地毡直播，首次采用 iPhone 配合 MacBook Pro 进行无线连接，成功为社交平台观众带来流畅清晰的画面。大会创作团队冀透过这种简便装置组合，应对不同拍摄情况，让直播过程更具机动性及操作简易，这场横跨两小时的电影盛事最终在 YouTube 平台稳定呈现。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2552-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2552-694x319.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="319" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2552-694x319.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2552-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834043.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1305250 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834043-396x580.jpg" alt="" width="396" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834043-396x580.jpg 396w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834043.jpg 615w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 396px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834030.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1305251 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834030-513x580.jpg" alt="" width="513" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834030-513x580.jpg 513w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834030.jpg 797w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 513px" /></a></p><p>今届直播技术配置上，大会选用两部 iPhone 16 Pro Max，无线连接到一部配备 M4 晶片的 MacBook Pro。手机端利用 NDI 应用程式（iOS），而 MacBook 则运行 Wirecast（macOS）软件，统一控制画面切换，进行现场直播。整个流程由大会网络直播合作伙伴及主持团队小薯茄负责，在官方及小薯茄两个 YouTube 频道同步播出。主持人除与红地毡嘉宾进行即时互动，大会技术人员亦可通过 MacBook 面板即时切换镜头角度，灵活掌握直播画面。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2558-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305254" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2558-694x319.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="319" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2558-694x319.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2558-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2562-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305255" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2562-694x319.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="319" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2562-694x319.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2562-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2564-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2564-694x319.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="319" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2564-694x319.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2564-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲当日直播画面</p><p>大会创作团队成员简君晋（《白日之下》导演）、黄锎（《填词 L》监制）、吴兆麟强调，今届首次试用这套便携式直播方案，明显提升了应变能力，尤其在户外不稳定环境下仍保持高水准输出。吴兆麟指出：「今次我们的 setup 配置，专门针对金针奖的网上直播，利用两部手机无线连接 Apple 面板，方便应对不同状况。今年特别选用 iPhone 来直播，发现机动性很高，整个设定亦简单，这次我们试验新方式，确保直播流程灵活流畅。」</p><p>整个直播历时超过两小时，从红地毡现场到主持与嘉宾对谈，画面顺畅无间断，亦体现了以手机配合电脑，打造高效户外直播方案的可行性。大会表示，未来将考虑持续采用这类轻便配置，为观众带来更贴近现场的即时体验。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2494-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2494-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2494-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_2494-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834024.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1305252 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834024-438x580.jpg" alt="" width="438" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834024-438x580.jpg 438w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042834024.jpg 679w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 438px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
